{"tid":1509531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［心都灰埋］你地點對得住所有義士？","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:51:14.000Z","uid":267470,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52243465ed952e7bcc30688e89919672aaf278a2","tid":1509531,"uid":267470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"六七月成個氣氛勁濃厚<br />\n文宣同人都一呼百應 要幫手既都即刻出黎<br />\n八月頭攪過靜坐集會 <br />\n由開group到出哂所有文宣 banner 搵media <br />\n只係用左48小時<br />\n個下知道我地有哩種信念一定會贏<br />\n但今日再攪集會 <br />\n話嬲話要攪既人好多<br />\n到真係做既得兩個人<br />\n逐個inbox 全部都唔覆<br />\n忙真係唔係大哂 個個都有自己既野要做<br />\n如果一個忙字就可以唔攪 咁被捕受傷既義士點？<br />\n大家可唔可以搵番初心<br />\n搵到一個理由堅持落去？<br />\n今次輸左我地咩都無哂<br />\n求下大家 唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\nWe never forget <br />\nWe never forgive"},{"pid":"2e7cf9b5db52adc749d30a73bd715e42ed713386","tid":1509531,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=797ec426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=107e918a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e77e7c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"2f9d88b84e8cd6faa37ce134d086a0bb436e2240","tid":1509531,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d22f3212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=2d07c1c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e9007e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=